CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. 6, reads: "'Main Street's' Four - Homewood Ave., the 'Main Street' which dissects the Homewood area, has several liquor dispensing establishments, including... (bottom rightt): . The Homewood Canteen, both in the 500 block... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: North Homewood Avenue with Homewood Canteen at 531, and Colonial Art and Decorating Co., at intersection of Susquehanna Street, Homewood
